    "※ 一般に睡眠不足は食欲増進ホルモンを増やし、ダイエットを妨げます。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* Schlafmangel erhöht im Allgemeinen die appetitanregenden Hormone und behindert das Abnehmen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* Generally speaking, lack of sleep increases the levels of appetite-stimulating hormones, which can hinder weight loss efforts."
          }
        },
        "en-GB" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* Generally speaking, lack of sleep increases appetite-stimulating hormones, hindering weight loss efforts."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* Generalmente, la falta de sueño aumenta las hormonas del apetito, dificultando la pérdida de peso."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* En général, le manque de sommeil augmente les hormones stimulant l'appétit, ce qui freine la perte de poids."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "※ 一般に睡眠不足は食欲増進ホルモンを増やし、ダイエットを妨げます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* 일반적으로 수면 부족은 식욕 증진 호르몬을 증가시켜 다이어트를 방해합니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* 通常来说，睡眠不足会增加食欲刺激激素，从而阻碍减重。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
